title: RMS Olympic from 1908 to 1935 in color! [A.I. enhanced]

sources.title: RMS Olympic from 1908 to 1935 in color! [A.I. enhanced]
sources.description: This film shows RMS Olympic from its construction in 1908 till it was scrapped in 1935. It is the only ship of the Titanic class to have been in service without mayor catastrophies. Sistership RMS Titanic sank on 14 April 1912 after hitting an iceberg on her maiden voyage and RMS Britannic sunk due to a German torpedo or sea mine.
